\chapquote{The Dreamlands}{I can't go back to yesterday because I was a different person then.\\ \textemdash Alice}

The home of the Five Queens, a land of infinite adventure and wonder that, for every Princess, lies just beyond the wall of sleep. The hopes, hearts and aspirations writ large into a patchwork of kingdoms and cities, ... and a land which, once, entrapped the Hopeful in webs of illusion, drawing them away from the real world's pain.

